data.title: Manor Independent School District
data.text:
Scholars build Spanish-speaking skills while engaging in a rigorous curriculum, which has been shown to result in improved academic performance.

Our high school scholars earn more associate degrees from our higher education partners than any other school district in the area.

Our district has been recognized by the Texas Art Education Association (TAEA) as a District of Distinction for Visual Arts for six years in a row, establishing it as one of the best in the state.
